        "ROB_DRIVER_BODY_SECONDARY_HEAVY_MACHINEGUN_DESCRIPTION": "Lance una granada que <style=cIsUtility>aturde</style> enemigos para 800% de daño.Original mod by public_ParticleSystem</i>",
        "ROB_DRIVER_BODY_SECONDARY_ROCKETLAUNCHER_NAME": "Tormenta",
        "ROB_DRIVER_BODY_SECONDARY_ROCKETLAUNCHER_DESCRIPTION": "Dispare una ráfaga rápida de cohetes para 300% de daño cada uno.Original mod by public_ParticleSystem</i>",
        "ROB_DRIVER_BODY_SECONDARY_ROCKETLAUNCHER_ALT_NAME": "Tormenta",
